title: 92: I Don't Got No Type ft. Paige Lorenze
description:
... bad bitches is the only thing that I like!
This week Sofia is joined by NYC's most eligible bachelorette, Paige Lorenze! Paige sits down with Sofia giving her the inside scoop on what it’s REALLY like to date celebs, and how to perfect the catch and release of bagging them. From dating a country superstar, to juicy details about dating Bachelorette heartthrob, Tyler Cameron. The two also discuss what it means to be a “girls girl” and the importance of remaining true to yourself regardless of public opinion. Finally, Sofia gives Paige some advice as to who her next celebrity catch should be and even helps her send a DM live on air. That’s what friends are for right? Sloots, it’s tea time
